  "comments": {
    "noble-hashes-version-conflict": "viem/wagmi need @noble/hashes 1.x (paths: ./sha2, ./utils); cosmjs and @mysten/sui need 2.x (paths: ./webcrypto.js). No single version satisfies both, so we let npm hoist each bundled copy."
